此寬閣的車站設有四個[[島式月台|島式月台]]和六條軌道<ref name="BklynEagle-INDFulton-Apr51936"/><ref name="BklynPaper-HoytPeeling-Mar2012">{{cite news|last1=O'Neill|first1=Natalie|title=Peeling ceiling is latest problem for G train riders|url=http://www.brooklynpaper.com/stories/35/13/dtg_hoytdamage_2012_03_30_bk.html|accessdate=August 28, 2016|work=Brooklyn Paper|date=March 29, 2012}}</ref><ref name=tracks/>。每個月台長660英呎，而北至南整個車站大約寬143英呎<ref name="BklynEagle-INDFulton-Apr51936"/>。中央一對軌道屬於跨城線（G線）。向東在拉法葉大道下方通過；向西則轉向南，在史密斯街下方併入[[IND第六大道線|IND第六大道線]]成為[[IND卡爾弗線|IND卡爾弗線]]<ref name="BklynEagle-INDFulton-Apr51936"/><ref name=tracks/><ref name=MTA-GLineReview-Append-2013>{{cite web|title=Review of the G Line: Appendices|url=http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/G_Appendices_7_10_13.pdf|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=October 28, 2015|date=July 10, 2013|archive-date=2016-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127233038/http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/G_Appendices_7_10_13.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由中央軌道算起的下一對軌道屬於福爾頓街線（A線和C線）。列車在這些軌道是左側開門，連接內側島式月台，而不是右側開門。向東C線列車分支往慢車軌道，然後所有四條軌道沿{{link-en|福爾頓街 (布魯克林)|Fulton Street (Brooklyn)|福爾頓街}}地下行走。向西快車軌道在傑伊街轉北，成為[[IND第八大道線|IND第八大道線]]<ref name="BklynEagle-INDFulton-Apr51936"/><ref name=tracks>{{NYCS const|trackref|468}}</ref><ref name=MTA-GLineReview-Append-2013/><ref name=MTA-ReviewAC-2015>{{cite web|title=Review of the A and C Lines|url=http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/pdf/AC_LineReview.pdf|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=January 19, 2016|date=December 11, 2015|archive-date=2020-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203061138/http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/pdf/AC_LineReview.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。福爾頓街線和跨城線沒有軌道連接<ref name=tracks/><ref name=MTA-GLineReview-Append-2013/><ref name=MTA-GLineReview-2013/>。

最外側的一對軌道：福爾頓街慢車軌道以及外側的兩個島式月台已經不作營運用途。向西軌道繼續在歇爾美角街下方前往已經退役、位於[[布魯克林高地_(布魯克林)|布魯克林高地]]的[[法庭街車站_(IND福爾頓街線)|法庭街]]車站，現時為[[紐約交通博物館|紐約交通博物館]]的館址<ref name="Lethem2007"/><ref name="BklynEagle-INDFulton-Apr51936"/><ref name=tracks/><ref name="BklynEagle-INDFulton-Apr51936">{{cite news|last1=Egan|first1=Leo|title=Brooklyn's New $53,000,000 Subway Line Ready to Open Wednesday Night|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/52660008/?terms=%22hoyt%2Bschermerhorn%22%2B%22station%22|accessdate=August 28, 2016|work=[[Brooklyn_Daily_Eagle|Brooklyn Daily Eagle]]|via=[[Newspapers.com|Newspapers.com]]|date=April 5, 1936|page=16}}</ref><ref name="ScoutingNY-Warriors3-2013"/><ref name="ScoutingNY-Warriors3-2013">{{cite news|title=The New York City Filming Locations of The Warriors – Part 3|url=http://www.scoutingny.com/the-new-york-city-filming-locations-of-the-warriors-part-3/|accessdate=September 10, 2016|work=Scouting New York|date=May 22, 2013}}</ref>。大部分月台層的天花板受水的破壞已經剝離<ref name="BklynPaper-HoytPeeling-Mar2012"/><ref>{{cite web|title=Audit Report on the New York City Transit Authority's Track Cleaning and Paining of the Subway Stations|url=http://comptroller.nyc.gov/wp-content/uploads/documents/FM14_071A.pdf|website=[[Government_of_New_York_City|nyc.gov]]|publisher=Office of the [[New_York_City_Comptroller|New York City Comptroller]]|accessdate=August 28, 2016|date=May 14, 2015}}</ref>。

受車站的寬度影響，車站南半部需要在歇爾美角街南側的私人土地下興建<ref name=BklynEagle-INDHoytCondemn-Jan1930/>。車站夾層位於車站北半部和歇爾美角街下方，包括一個{{link-en|紐約市交通警察|New York City Transit Police}}局，同時是紐約市交通警察交通30區總部所在地 <ref name="Lethem2007" /><ref>{{cite web|title=Transit Bureau - Transit District 30|url=http://www.nyc.gov/html/nypd/html/transit_bureau/district_30.shtml|website=[[Government_of_New_York_City|nyc.gov]]|publisher=[[New_York_City_Police_Department|New York City Police Department]]|accessdate=August 28, 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160830011242/http://www.nyc.gov/html/nypd/html/transit_bureau/district_30.shtml|archivedate=2016-08-30}}</ref>以及若干[[紐約市公共運輸局|紐約市公共運輸局]]辦公室所在地。

